Ing '''{{audio|Tripura.ogg|Tripura}}''' ( [[Bengali language|Bengali]]: ত্রিপুরা) metung yang [[Estadu ampong teritoriu ning India|estadu]] king [[:en:North-East India|Pangulu-aslagang India]], a maki lapad a 4,036 [[square mile|sq. mi.]] or 10,453 [[km²]].<ref>[http://www.north-east-india.com/tripura/tripura-history.html Tripura History]</ref> Ing Tripura padurutan ne ning [[Bangladesh]] king [[pangulu]], [[mauli]], ampong [[albugan]]. Atiu no man king [[aslagan]] deng [[Assam]] ampong [[Mizoram]], a estadu ning [[India]]. Atiu king [[Agartala]] ing kayang tungku o capitoliu, at deng manimuna nang amanu ila pin deng [[:en:Bengali language|Bengali]] ampong [[:en:Kokborok|Kokborok]] (a ausan da mu namang Tripuri). Sadia, metung yang magsariling [[:en:Twipra Kingdom|Kayarian a Tripuri]]<ref>[http://tripura.nic.in/kt3.htm Govt. of Tripura]</ref>. Miabe ya king timawang [[India]] aniang [[15 Octubri]] [[1949]] kapamilatan ning [[:en:Tripura Merger Agreement|Tripura Merger Agreement]]. Ausan de mu namang '''Hill Tippera''' (ininglis a bersion ning '''[[:en:Tipra|Tipra]]''') aniang [[:en:British Raj|panaun ning pamaniakup ning Britania]].<ref>[http://dsal.uchicago.edu/reference/gazetteer/pager.html?objectid=DS405.1.I34_V13_124.gif Hill Tippera - History] ''[[The Imperial Gazetteer of India]]'', 1909, v. 13, p. 118.</ref><ref name="britannica">[http://www.1911encyclopedia.org/Hill_Tippera Hill Tippera], from [[Encyclopædia Britannica Eleventh Edition]].</ref>. Maki amlat yang miraras maigit king 2500 banua at sasaklo kareng 186 a ari{{Fact|date=February 2009}}.   
